## Custom Objects Summary

| # | Object | API Name | Record Name | Format |
|---|--------|----------|-------------|--------|
| 1 | Job | `Job__c` | Job Number | Auto Number `JOB-{0000}` |
| 2 | Candidate | `Candidate__c` | Candidate Name | Text |
| 3 | Application | `Application__c` | Application Number | Auto Number `APP-{0000}` |
| 4 | Interview | `Interview__c` | Interview Number | Auto Number `INT-{0000}` |
| 5 | Offer | `Offer__c` | Offer Number | Auto Number `OFF-{0000}` |

---

## Object Metadata XML

### Job__c.object-meta.xml
```xml
<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>
<CustomObject xmlns=\"http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata\">
    <label>Job</label>
    <pluralLabel>Jobs</pluralLabel>
    <nameField>
        <displayFormat>JOB-{0000}</displayFormat>
        <label>Job Number</label>
        <type>AutoNumber</type>
    </nameField>
    <deploymentStatus>Deployed</deploymentStatus>
    <sharingModel>ReadWrite</sharingModel>
    <enableActivities>true</enableActivities>
    <enableReports>true</enableReports>
    <enableSearch>true</enableSearch>
</CustomObject>
```

