## Setup Path (Salesforce UI)
**Setup → Object Manager → Create → Custom Object**

For each object:
1. Define label, plural label, API name.
2. Choose record name type (Text / Auto Number).
3. Enable Reports, Activities, Search, Field History Tracking.
4. Set sharing model.
